<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:321\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.321</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:328\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">328</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁ δ᾽ ὅρκος ἦν τοῦ ς. ἐπανάτασις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg035.perseus-grc1:1285b:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pol.\">Pol.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1285b12</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; used as a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stick</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cudgel</tr_> to punish the refractory, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:199\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.199</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:265\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">265</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:28\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">O.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.28</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:811\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OT\">OT</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">811</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n94808.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> as a symbol of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">royalty, kingly power</tr_>, etc., <bibl n=\"urn:cts: